主任还称，学校也会介入调解此事，尽量协商将此事解决，好好教育孩子。 有网友认为，家长不该给孩子绑那么大额的银行卡，为了方便我也给孩子绑了一张空卡，一次最多就往里转二百块钱。也有网友表示，不管是女孩子主动开口要的红包，还是男孩子自己主动发的红包，都应该教育孩子这钱不应该要。 来源：聚焦新闻"},"attached_info":"Cj8IpP7y/bOSib5QEAMaCDcwNzE0OTk0IMnVoIoGMCU49wNABnIJNDg3OTUwMDYxeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"587 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-13770c9fda2ff9253f6f7bd2125f778c_b.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"7_1632204550.7963054","card_id":"Q_488003026","target":{"id":488003026,"title":"如何看待9月20日币圈全线暴跌?","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/488003026","type":"question","created":1632141797,"answer_count":109,"follower_count":415,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[16712,121064,210433],"comment_count":20,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"时间:2021年9月20日"},"attached_info":"Cj8IpP7y/bOSib5QEAMaCDcwNzI2Nzg5IOWDoooGMBQ4nwNAB3IJNDg4MDAzMDI2eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"427 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-43c03280b26f9f217f0f9c25c2750324_720w.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"8_1632204550.7968545","card_id":"Q_487928094","target":{"id":487928094,"title":"澳大利亚“潜艇门”，为什么能撕开西方阵营？法国召回美澳大使，又释放了什么信号？莫里斯为何会突然反水？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/487928094","type":"question","created":1632109613,"answer_count":38,"follower_count":128,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[704,30958,105508],"comment_count":2,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"Cj8IpP7y/bOSib5QEAMaCDcwNzEwMTYzIK2IoIoGMAI4gAFACHIJNDg3OTI4MDk0eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"414 万热度","trend":0,"debut":true,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"